&lt;h3>✅ File Handling and Exceptions&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="-file-handling-and-exceptions">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#-file-handling-and-exceptions" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h3>&lt;ul>
